1
00:00:00,029 --> 00:00:03,132
[Music]

2
00:00:03,132 --> 00:00:07,804
You may have heard about the
infamous Miller-Urey experiment back in 1953,

3
00:00:07,804 --> 00:00:12,408
in which electricity was added to
certain gases under specialized conditions.

4
00:00:12,408 --> 00:00:17,380
This was intended to show how
life could spontaneously arise without God.

5
00:00:17,380 --> 00:00:19,482
But the experiment
actually showed that it took

6
00:00:19,482 --> 00:00:22,285
a great deal of
intelligence to set up conditions

7
00:00:22,285 --> 00:00:26,522
that produced mostly a lot
of tar and just a few amino acids.

8
00:00:26,522 --> 00:00:28,925
This is a long way from a living self.

9
00:00:28,925 --> 00:00:31,361
Here are some of the
problems with that experiment.

10
00:00:31,361 --> 00:00:33,930
First, there were
starting assumptions about what

11
00:00:33,930 --> 00:00:37,533
gases would have been
present on the primordial Earth,

12
00:00:37,533 --> 00:00:39,969
and these didn't
include oxygen, which tends to

13
00:00:39,969 --> 00:00:43,439
destroy chemical bonds,
preventing anything from forming.

14
00:00:43,439 --> 00:00:47,944
Now, since then, evidence indicates
that oxygen likely was present at the time.

15
00:00:47,944 --> 00:00:51,714
So because it didn't
accurately simulate the Earth's atmosphere,

16
00:00:51,714 --> 00:00:54,317
it's pretty much
irrelevant as an experiment,

17
00:00:54,317 --> 00:00:57,053
and those amino
acids could not have formed.

18
00:00:57,053 --> 00:01:00,156
Not only that, many
molecules required for life exist

19
00:01:00,156 --> 00:01:03,559
in two forms that look
like mirror images of each other,

20
00:01:03,559 --> 00:01:05,161
like your left and right hands.

21
00:01:05,161 --> 00:01:08,731
This is called chirality,
from the Greek word for "hand."

22
00:01:08,731 --> 00:01:10,800
The Miller-Urey experiment produced equal

23
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:13,836
amounts of left and
right-handed forms of amino acids.

24
00:01:13,836 --> 00:01:17,340
Yeah, but all amino
acids and proteins are left-handed,

25
00:01:17,340 --> 00:01:22,278
while all sugars in DNA and RNA
and in metabolic pathways are right-handed.

26
00:01:22,278 --> 00:01:26,182
Random chemical
reactions won't produce 100%

27
00:01:26,182 --> 00:01:28,885
left-handed amino
acids that are needed for life.

28
00:01:28,885 --> 00:01:31,120
This is just one
example of thousands where

29
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:35,758
evolutionists have major
problems explaining how life originated.

30
00:01:35,758 --> 00:01:39,796
But evolution continues to be
promoted as established scientific fact.

31
00:01:39,796 --> 00:01:40,396
It's not.

32
00:01:40,396 --> 00:01:40,830
No.

